  m_Name: SporeEvent
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Mechanomics.Core::EventData
  title: The Mold is Back. Again.
  description: My asshole roommate went trespassing in a quarantine spore zone and
    tracked that shit in our apartment. Our landlord's gonna be pissed. Can you guys
    send a robot to clear this out? Feel free to use drastic measures.
  suggestedSize: 1
  behaviour:
    rid: 3076055974353305677
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds:
    - rid: 3076055974353305677
      type: {class: SkillEvent, ns: , asm: Mechanomics.Core}
      data:
        requirements:
        - stat: 0
          amount: 15
        - stat: 2
          amount: 15
        cashReward: 1500
        quotaReward: 1
        cashPenalty: 1500
        successText: Since last week's quarantining of mutated mold spores on the
          east side, citizens have reported sightings of mutant mold within their
          own homes. Luckily for them, MetaMech has announced a coordinated effort
          to clean up these mold patches and keep our cities' housing safe.
        failureText: Last week's mutated mold spores are taking over city apartments
          after a breach in local quarantine procedures. MetaMech pilots are allegedly
          involved in the spread, with MetaMech refusing comment on the situation.
          CityNews12 reccommends that all citizens follow CDC guidelines during these
          times.
